Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:12.27,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:730140,732270}Sorry for the trouble.{NOTE:や、お手数をかけました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:14.40,Default,Blond,0,0,0,,{TIME:732270,734400}Just a moment.{NOTE:Ah, just a moment.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:18.86,Default,Blond,0,0,0,,{TIME:734400,738860}Why don't you practice at the Central Gymnasium?{NOTE:どうしてセントラル体育館の練習場を使わないのですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.03,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:738860,741030}You see…{NOTE:や、それは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:23.74,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:741030,743740}I'm in a hurry, so I'll need to excuse myself.{NOTE:ちょっと先を急ぎますんで失礼します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:32.00,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:748280,752000}We need to do this training in secret.{NOTE:この練習は是非とも秘密のうちに行う必要がある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:36.25,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:752000,756250}If we do it at the Central Gymnasium and let the reporters near us…{NOTE:セントラル体育館の練習場でやって新聞社などの目に触れたら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:38.96,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:756250,758960}…all of our effort will go to waste.{NOTE:…それこそ全ての努力が無駄になりかねるのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:46.43,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:761760,766430}However, to think that there's\Nno other place where we could practice…{NOTE:とは言ってもその練習をすべき肝心のコートがないとは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:54.60,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:773390,774600}Hey!{NOTE:Hey!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:55.94,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:774600,775940}Hippie coach!{NOTE:ヒッピーコーチ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.28,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:780940,783280}Wait, you're from the American team, aren't you?{NOTE:あなたは確かアメリカチームの…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.24,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:784320,786240}Yes, I'm their captain, Cassie.{NOTE:Yes。キャプテンのキャシーです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:07.28,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:786240,787280}Hippie coach.{NOTE:ヒッピーコーチ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:11.29,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:789240,791290}Um, "hippie coach" is rather embarrassing.{NOTE:しかしヒッピーコーチとは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:13.58,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:791290,793580}Oh, I'm sorry.{NOTE:あ、ごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:16.50,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:793580,796500}Hippie coach is your nickname.{NOTE:ヒッピーコーチはあなたにニックネームです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.38,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:796500,798380}That's what we called you within our team.{NOTE:私達そう呼んでいたのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.92,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:798380,799920}I see. Haha.{NOTE:これは。ハハハ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:24.84,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:802420,804840}I wonder what Coach is doing?{NOTE:どうしたの、コーチは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:27.43,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:804840,807430}He probably can't find an empty court.{NOTE:きっとコートが借りられないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:30.76,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:807430,810760}If we can't practice the two-stage reception…{NOTE:もし二段レシーブの練習ができなかったら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.97,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:810760,812970}If we can't master it…!{NOTE:二段レシーブがマスターできなかったら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:50.95,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:825070,830950}I'll end up on the court just like Češka…\Nno, even worse than that.{NOTE:私もチェシカのように…いいえ、それ以上に惨めにコートに叩きつけられるに決まっている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.91,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:831330,834910}It's not just me. Everyone in here—{NOTE:いいえ、私ばかりがここにいるみんなもコートに叩きつけられて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:58.04,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:836040,838040}Oh, Coach!?{NOTE:あ、コーチ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:838830,840590}Really?{NOTE:本当ですかコーチ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:01.38,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:840590,841380}Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.26,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:841380,844260}Cassie from the American team got her father to put in a request.{NOTE:アメリカチームのキャプテンキャシーのお父さんの請いで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:06.63,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:844260,846630}The Rotary Club will let us borrow us a gym.{NOTE:…ロータリークラブの体育館が借りられることになった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:11.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:848720,851760}Actually, Coach, we have great news, too.{NOTE:実はコーチこっちにも素晴らしいニュースがあるんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:14.52,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:853510,854520}What?{NOTE:何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:16.48,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:854520,856480}The South Korean team's captain, Sai, is here?{NOTE:韓国のキャプテン、サイが来てくれたって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:22.36,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:859770,862360}Sai-kun. We really appreciate this.{NOTE:サイ君。強力本当に感謝する。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:24.23,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:862360,864230}I was free anyway.{NOTE:私もどうせ暇なんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:29.78,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:864230,869780}And I'm very happy that I get to play with the All-Japan team once more.{NOTE:それよりオールジャパンは相手にもう一度バレーが出来るなんて大変幸せです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:34.29,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:869780,874290}Cassie not only went through\Na lot of effort to let us borrow this court…{NOTE:キャシーはこのコートを借りるために色々奔走してくれたばかりじゃなく…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:39.79,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:874290,879790}…but she also gathered members of her team\Nto accommodate us with a proper practice session.{NOTE:…どうせ練習をするなら実践に即して行った方がいいだろうとメンバーを集めてくれたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:40.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:879790,880670}Cassie!{NOTE:キャシー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.04,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:880670,882040}Thank you very much.{NOTE:Thank you very much.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:48.17,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:882040,888170}We don't have to go to school until the end\Nof the World Championships anyway.{NOTE:どうせ私達はこの世界選手権が終わるまでは学校に行かなくてもいいことになっています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.30,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:888170,890300}So we're all free.{NOTE:ですから暇なのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:54.76,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,{TIME:890300,894760}Most of us are not as strong as the Soviet team, though.{NOTE:最も私達はソ連チームのように強くはありませんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:15:00.35,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:896140,900350}Ladies. Czechoslovakia lost 3 to 0 to the Soviet Union.{NOTE:諸君。チェコはソ連に3対0のストレートで敗れた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:04.98,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:900350,904980}Therefore, as expected, our opponent in the final match tomorrow will be the Soviet Union.{NOTE:したがって明日の決勝戦の相手は予想通りソ連と決まった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:07.15,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:906150,907150}Listen up.{NOTE:いいか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:16.24,Default,Inokuma,1,1,0,,{TIME:907150,916240}{\fs40}We'll now commence the two-stage reception training to counter Borchinskaya's killer spike in tomorrow's finals.{NOTE:これからはその決勝戦の相手ソ連のボルチンスカヤのあの殺人スパイクを見事レシーブするための二段レシーブの練習を行う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:916240,918120}Yes sir!{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:20.12,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:918120,920120}The basis of the two-stage reception is this…{NOTE:二段レシーブとは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:25.25,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:923170,925250}Oh, he's using chess?{NOTE:あ？チェスだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:30.26,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:925250,930260}Let's say Borchinskaya performs her spike from here.{NOTE:ボルチンスカヤのスパイクが例えばここに打ち込まれた時。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:33.55,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:930260,933550}The receiver repels her spike backwards.{NOTE:レシーバーはそのスパイクを後ろへ弾き返す。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:38.56,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:933550,938560}At the same time the player here runs out of the court and sends it back.{NOTE:と同時にこの一にいる選手は一目散にコートの外へ駆け出す。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:40.48,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:938560,940480}They'll need to be much faster than the ball.{NOTE:ボールよりも早くな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:42.02,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:940480,942020}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:42.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:942020,942850}Runs o—{NOTE:駆け出す…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.77,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:942850,944770}Err, runs out of the court?{NOTE:あの、コートの外へ駆け出す？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:47.11,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:944770,947110}Next is this player.{NOTE:次にこの選手だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:02.62,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:961330,962628}Huh? Professor.{NOTE:あ？先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:04.00,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:963040,964000}Professor!{NOTE:先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.54,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:964000,965540}Professor Hongou!{NOTE:本郷先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.59,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:965540,967592}Oh, it's you, Ichinose?{NOTE:よ。一ノ瀬か。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.38,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:969050,970380}Good morning, Professor.{NOTE:おはようございます先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.84,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:970380,972840}Morning. Starting the day with a stroll?{NOTE:おはよう。朝の散歩か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:14.43,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:972840,974430}Yes. You too, Professor?{NOTE:はい。先生もですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:15.68,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:974430,975680}Heh. You could say that.{NOTE:ふふん。ま、な。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:24.35,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:978970,984350}I just heard in the news that\Nthe Soviet team got into the finals, after all.{NOTE:今ニュースーで聞いたんですけど、明日の決勝戦相手はやはりソ連チームに決まりましたね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:35.16,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:992450,995160}I wonder what Ayuhara-kun and her team are doing now?{NOTE:今頃鮎原君達どうしてるかな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.62,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:995160,997620}I was just thinking the same thing.{NOTE:今僕もそれを考えてたところだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:40.95,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:997620,1000950}I guess they're taking a good rest\Nto prepare for the final game tomorrow.{NOTE:明日の決勝戦に備えてゆっくり休養をとってるんでしょうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:43.08,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000950,1003080}No, that's not Inokuma's style.{NOTE:いいえ、猪野熊のことだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:45.75,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003080,1005750}I bet he's giving everyone one last drill.{NOTE:恐らく最後の練習でみんなを絞ってるだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:52.26,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008920,1012260}Who do you think is going to win, Professor?{NOTE:どうでしょう。先生から見て、勝差はありますか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:53.34,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012260,1013340}Hm.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:56.97,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013340,1016970}Well, it's obvious that the All-Japan team\Nis very strong, just like Inokuma's pride.{NOTE:オールジャパンは猪野熊が自慢するだけあって確かに強い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:00.06,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016970,1020060}But the Soviets have become stronger, too.{NOTE:しかしソ連も前より強くなっている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:03.64,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020060,1023640}That iron block and Borchinskaya's spike.{NOTE:あの鉄壁のブロックとボルチンスカヤのスパイク。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:06.48,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023640,1026480}I wonder how Inokuma plans to counter these?{NOTE:果たして猪野熊あれをどう破るつもりだろうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:28.08,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045920,1048080}Run faster!{NOTE:もっと速く走れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.54,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048080,1049540}Y-Yes sir!{NOTE:は、はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:32.55,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1050630,1052550}– Next!\N– Yes sir!{NOTE:—次！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:42.56,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060050,1062560}One more minute. Hurry up!{NOTE:後一秒。速く走れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:43.77,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062560,1063770}Y-Yes sir.{NOTE:は、はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:48.27,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063770,1068270}When I think about it, it is kind of weird to hold races in reception training.{NOTE:考えてみるとレシーブの練習に駆けっこなんて可笑しいよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:49.77,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1068270,1069770}Hahaha.{NOTE:ははは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:51.86,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1069770,1071860}– Hey! Quit running your mouth!\N– Yes sir.{NOTE:—こら！XX聞くんじゃない！\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:52.65,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071860,1072650}Next!{NOTE:次！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:07.08,Default,Hotel,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083910,1087080}The All-Japan team isn't here yet.{NOTE:オールジャパンのみなさんまだですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:08.79,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087080,1088790}They haven't returned to the hotel yet.{NOTE:未だホテルに帰ってないそうだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:09.58,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088790,1089580}Really?{NOTE:未だ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:14.96,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089580,1094960}The Russians returned from their training long ago\Nand are holding a team meeting in their hotel.{NOTE:全くソ連チームは総仕上げの練習も終わり今頃はホテルでミーティングでもやっているというのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:18.72,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094960,1098720}I really don't have the slightest idea where our volleyball girls could have gone.{NOTE:我がオールジャパンのメメはどこへ蒸発しちゃったのかな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:24.02,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098720,1104020}You don't think they'd go sightseeing before such an important game, do you?{NOTE:まさか大事な決勝戦の前にニューヨークー見物としゃれこんでるんじゃないだろうな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:28.02,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104020,1108020}Well, Coach Inokuma surely doesn't make reporting any easier for us, either way.{NOTE:全く俺達新聞記者XXだよな、あの猪野熊ってコーチは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.02,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108350,1109020}Next!{NOTE:次！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:41.28,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116440,1121280}Use your lower body more! Make sure\Nto stay calm at the moment of receiving.{NOTE:もっと腰をXX！レシーブする瞬間体を鎮めるような気持ちを忘れるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.03,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121280,1122030}Yes sir.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:43.12,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1122030,1123120}– Next!\N– Yes sir!{NOTE:—次！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:30.16,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168500,1170160}How many times do I need to repeat myself!?{NOTE:何度言ったら分かるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:33.21,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170160,1173210}That ribbon isn't there just for elegance!{NOTE:あのリボンは伊達に付けてあるんじゃないぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:37.42,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173210,1177420}Don't try to return it to an attacker right away and aim it at that ribbon!{NOTE:アタッカーに返そうとせずあのリボン目掛けてボールを飛ばせばいいんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.51,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177420,1178510}Okay.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:11.71,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210750,1211710}No good.{NOTE:駄目だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:14.42,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211710,1214420}Ayuhara, what were you doing at the camp in Miyazaki?{NOTE:鮎原。宮崎の合宿で何をやっていたんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.46,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214420,1216460}What are we going to do\Nif you can't even do this much?{NOTE:これぐらいのことはできないでどうする？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:17.34,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216460,1217340}I'm sorry, sir.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:02.09,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259040,1262090}The remaining problem is the Soviets' iron block.{NOTE:残る問題はソ連の鉄壁ブロックだが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.43,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262090,1264430}But I don't think there's that much to be afraid of.{NOTE:これとX別に恐れることはない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:08.76,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264430,1268760}When Captain Shellenina turns\Nto Borchinskaya, she can no longer block you.{NOTE:キャプテンシェレーニナバックに回ってしまえば鉄壁ブロックはできないのだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:11.72,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268760,1271720}We can earn points by targeting that opening.{NOTE:その隙を狙ってポイントを稼げばいいんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:16.06,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271720,1276060}This is the end of the meeting tonight,\Nbut one last word.{NOTE:これで今夜のミーティングは終わるが最後に一言。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:20.15,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276060,1280150}Thanks to everyone's efforts we managed to figure out the two-stage reception.{NOTE:みんなの努力のおかげで二段レシーブもどうやらかっこがついた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:23.53,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281610,1283530}Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.78,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283530,1284780}Kakinouchi.{NOTE:垣之内。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:25.45,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284780,1285450}Yes.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:26.86,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285450,1286860}Sanjou.{NOTE:三条。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:27.87,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286860,1287870}Hayakawa.{NOTE:早川。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:28.78,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287870,1288780}Yoshimura.{NOTE:吉村。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:29.58,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288780,1289580}Arai.{NOTE:新井。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:30.49,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289580,1290490}Noda.{NOTE:野田。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:31.37,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290490,1291370}Ootsuki.{NOTE:大槻。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:32.37,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291370,1292370}Miyatsu.{NOTE:宮津。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:33.79,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292370,1293790}Mishima.{NOTE:三島。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:37.37,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293790,1297370}Everyone of you held out well so far.{NOTE:皆最後の最後までよく俺についてきてくれた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:38.25,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297370,1298250}You have my gratitude.{NOTE:礼を言う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:45.47,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299630,1305470}Give everything you have in tomorrow's finals and play without regrets.{NOTE:明日の決勝戦は自分達の持っている全てを叩き込んで悔いのない試合をやってくれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:48.89,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305470,1308890}That's all I want from you right now.{NOTE:今の俺がお前達に望むのはそれだけだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:49.55,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1308890,1309550}Yes sir.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:56.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314140,1316100}It's open.{NOTE:どうぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:57.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316100,1317190}Sai-san!?{NOTE:サイさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:59.15,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317190,1319150}Oh, it's you, Sai-san.{NOTE:ま、サイさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:00.44,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319150,1320440}Coach Inokuma.{NOTE:猪野熊コーチ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.52,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320440,1321520}Everyone.{NOTE:それからみなさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:03.15,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321520,1323150}I came here to say good-bye.{NOTE:お別れに来ました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:05.61,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323150,1325610}Our team is flying home tonight.{NOTE:私達のチームは今夜の飛行機で帰ります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:06.65,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1325610,1326650}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:09.49,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326650,1329490}I really wanted to see tomorrow's finals.{NOTE:明日の決勝戦是非見たいのですが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:13.66,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329490,1333660}But unfortunately we lost twice in a row,\Nso we have to go home.{NOTE:二回戦で負けた私達残念ですが帰らなければなりません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.66,0:22:18.21,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333660,1338210}So, Sai-san, you used up all of your remaining time here to practice with us…?{NOTE:じゃ、サイさんは帰国前の貴重な時間を割いて私達の練習を。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:21.96,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339000,1341960}Well, I didn't come to America to play around.{NOTE:だって私はアメリカに遊びに来たのではありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:23.71,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341960,1343710}I came here to play volleyball.{NOTE:バレーをしに来たんですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:29.72,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1348260,1349720}Captain Ayuhara.{NOTE:キャプテン鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:31.60,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1349720,1351600}Good luck tomorrow.{NOTE:明日はきっと頑張ってください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:34.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353100,1354310}Thank you.{NOTE:有難う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:37.27,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355390,1357270}We're fellow Asians, after all.{NOTE:同じアジアの兄弟。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:39.19,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357270,1359190}Everyone of All-Japan.{NOTE:オールジャパンの皆さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:41.52,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1359190,1361520}Please do your best in our stead.{NOTE:私の分まで頑張ってください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.52,0:22:42.94,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1361520,1362940}Thank you, Sai-san.{NOTE:有難うサイさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.94,0:22:45.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362940,1365150}Please give my regards to the Korean team.{NOTE:韓国チームの皆さんにもよろしく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:02.13,Default,Sai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1381040,1382130}Alright, let's go.{NOTE:さ、行きましょう。}
