Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:13.26,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1391050,1393260}And now Sai-kun's sincerity.{NOTE:そして今またこのサイ君の真心。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:17.14,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1394220,1397140}There are some things I've long forgotten during the last decade.{NOTE:俺はこの十数年間忘れていたものを。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:20.56,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1397140,1400560}Now it feels like they're all slowly coming back to me.{NOTE:いましっかりと取り戻してXX気がする。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.56,0:23:22.31,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1400560,1402310}The beauty of dreams and the human heart.{NOTE:人の心の美しさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:26.28,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1404650,1406280}Well, girls.{NOTE:さ、みんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.28,0:23:29.07,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1406280,1409070}We have last mission.{NOTE:その心を一つにしてやろう。}
