Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:38.00,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1417080,1418000}We'll do it.{NOTE:やるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:39.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1418000,1419080}We will do our best.{NOTE:頑張るわ。}
